 of reanalysis data.
 On the other hand, reproducing the arrival of cold fronts is a key factor
 in forecasting extreme fire weather 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "Mills2005,Engel2013"

\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "Mills2005"

\end_inset

